    "data": [
        {
            "title": "瑞士央行維持利率在零水平 自2024年初以來首次停止降息",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"639\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/G46.Z5aRY6a.r4xcJM1dBg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzOTtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/6c1c068a875cf84d5f44a62a317e80d4\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 瑞士央行維持借貸成本不變，停止寬鬆周期，官員們避免恢復負利率。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">央行官員周四將基準利率維持在零水平，這與彭博調查24位經濟學家中絕大多數人的預測一致。唯一一位持不同觀點的經濟學家預計會降息。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「通膨壓力與上一季度相比幾乎沒有變化。」央行在一份聲明中表示，「瑞士央行將繼續監測形勢，並在必要時調整貨幣政策，以確保價格穩定。」</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"639\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/NXNMX8fqHAe40BJYlf3uYQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzOTtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/bad5f5f5abe7d02163513ba5a3180afe\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在此之前自2024年3月開始，央行連續六次降息。官員們一直表示，重新引入全球唯一的負利率對金融體系造成的損害，意味著他們需要對此類舉措設置比更傳統降息更高的門檻。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-45e267be-8f88-3e1b-ae30-8b31a8fecd5f-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">雖然通膨率可能接近0-2%區間的底部，但最近0.2%的讀數仍高於瑞士央行的預測。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">消息公佈後，瑞郎兌歐元匯率基本持平，報1歐元兌0.9341瑞郎。兌美元匯率持穩於0.7956。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「關稅可能會特別抑制出口和投資。」瑞士央行表示，「瑞士的經濟前景仍然不確定。主要風險是美國貿易政策和全球經濟發展。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">官員發布了新的消費者價格指數成長展望，與之前的預測一致。他們預測今年消費者價格指數平均成長0.2%，2026年0.5%，2027年0.7%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題SNB Keeps Rate at Zero in First Easing Halt Since Early 2024 (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Harumi Ichikura、Joel Rinneby、Naomi Tajitsu、Paula Doenecke、Jan-Henrik Foerster.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">(新增最後三段)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%91%9E%E5%A3%AB%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C%E7%B6%AD%E6%8C%81%E5%88%A9%E7%8E%87%E5%9C%A8%E9%9B%B6%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3-%E8%87%AA2024%E5%B9%B4%E5%88%9D%E4%BB%A5%E4%BE%86%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E5%81%9C%E6%AD%A2%E9%99%8D%E6%81%AF-080202579.html",
